property.description: READY FOR MAUI BEACH LIFE? Live in or rent out this gorgeous 2bdr/2bath condominium at Kahana Manor. A condo community with all the conveniences right out your doorstep. Restaurants, Convenience Store, Vacation Sundries & more all across the street from the ocean. This lovely condo home comes furnished down to the dishes and linens. An open plan greets you and so do the tropical breezes that make this a refreshing location in the complex. The open plan condo had all new floors added in 2017. The light tile with light wood style is perfect for the beach look. The main bedroom is light & spacious with it's own en-suite bath. Both baths have full tub/shower, new mirrors and classic vanities added in 2017. The condo has washer/dryer inside the unit. The complex features private swimming pool & bbq area in addition to the shops on the main level.
